missions/beyond-de-giorgi/steps/step-002/REASONING.md:42:  - Step 2 should proceed, but only around the hybrid transport-plus-coherence route centered on `direction coherence + tube persistence`, with other geometry ingredients treated as comparators or fragility screens rather than primary observables.
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/refined/chain-02.md:5:Do not ask whether NS has "the SQG commutator." Ask the narrower question:
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/refined/chain-02.md:20:This branch is still about whether the exact NS algebra can be operationalized into a better nonlinear mechanism, but it is no longer a general search over pretty identities. It is an estimate-first screen tied directly to the mission bottleneck and separated from geometry-first Beltrami analysis.
