missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-03.md:12:- a sharp negative result showing that local Beltrami geometry is too fragile to buy any real depletion.
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-03.md:23:- Action: synthesize Constantin-Fefferman style criteria and define the quantitative observables this mission cares about: vorticity-direction modulus, local Beltrami deficit, and concentration of the high-`|omega|` set.
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-03.md:25:- Kill condition: if the known geometric criteria are too nonlocal or too strong to connect to any local Beltrami quantity, stop and write that mismatch down explicitly.
